data.description: POOL! Be Ready for Summer. Amazing, Five Bedroom, 2.5 Bath Colonial with Finished Basement in the Lovely Hunters Gate neighborhood! Enter the foyer and you'll know this home is for you! Formal living area to the left and formal dining room to the right. Pass through to the back of the home and you'll find a spacious living room, kitchen area with slider to the amazing backyard with Saltwater Pool (16x34, 9 foot deep) with newer liner and cover. The back yard is surrounded by a Vinyl fence. The downstairs is completed with a half bath, laundry room, and 2 car garage.  Upstairs you'll find a large primary bedroom with dual walk in closets and spacious bathroom with jet tub and stall shower along with a Nursery Door that leads to the adjoining room. There are 4 additional spacious bedrooms and another full bath. Home has a 7 zone Sprinkler system. Close to shopping and all major roadways,
